                    <div class="col-span-2 col-start-3 m-1 rounded-md bg-ink-900 text-white px-1.5 py-1 font-semibold truncate">Varga D.</div>
                    <div class="col-span-3 col-start-5 m-1 rounded-md bg-leaf-50 text-leaf-700 px-1.5 py-1 font-semibold ring-1 ring-leaf-200 border border-dashed border-leaf-300 truncate">passzív (ózon zár)</div>
                  </div>
